name: FREAKOLOCO! #66
description: This little gnome was hired for the lead role in the movie Lord of the Gems, but the producers of the movie didn't know that the stone they gave him as a prop was actually magic. Before he started working on the movie, he had lived a normal life with his wife and two hundred children and sold mushroom crackers in FREAKOLAND! and around the world.  Now he is in a catatonic state of staring at the magic stone, and when anyone comes near, he looks like a demon, trying to protect it. We hope that some warriors help him get the stone to where it belongs.  Type: Creature / Edition: 3rd / Alignment: True Neutral / Height: 118 cm / Weight: 36 kg / Strength: 30 / Dexterity: 30 / Constitution: 45 / Intelligence: 30 / Wisdom: 25 / Charisma: 80.
